reviewText: Very cool movie. Two very cool song's. Not in english. Must use subtitle's. One of my favorite's. No dislike's.
A very funny but dark farce on a young Pakistani who is determined to come to the USA and a bin Laden look-alike who is a poultry farmer. Bit dated now that the real Bin Laden has been dispatched.
Goofy comedy about some folks struggling for a break who think they've found it when they fake a video of Osama bin Laden. Light comedy with a few soft political jabs.
